message:
Documentation and readability improvements.

Modify the documentation to make it slightly easier to follow the flow
of class inheritence.

Prepare for release with improved docs.

Adds some additional detail for getting started, and
clean up some setup file to prepare for initial release.

Add support for subscribing to events

Uses the 'Guides: Subscribe to Events' docs to
allow the command line tool to fetch events using
the google cloud pubsub APIs.
Add instructions for where to donate.

Check in development environment reqs

Set up the virtual environment following the instructions in this tutorial:
https://developer.akamai.com/blog/2017/06/21/how-building-virtual-python-environment
Use flake8 to address test lint errors.

Improve releases, unpinning, etc

Don't pin python versions for common libraries.
Include requirements.txt in the source release

fixes=2
Fix errors in Fetching Data section
Add README replacing commands with pre-commit
Remove release instructions since it is now automated on github releases
Adjust flake8 package groupings to send in single group for version pinning
Exclude command line tool from code coverage
